Title : Stephen Thraves
Text : '''Stephen Thraves''' is a British children's author. The author of over 200 books, he is the creator of ''[[Fetch the Vet]]'', a 26 episode animation for pre-school which aired on [[ITV (TV channel)|ITV]] between 1999 and 2001. He also wrote eight ''[[The Famous Five (novel series)|Famous Five]]'' adventure game books based on [[Enid Blyton]]'s major series, published by [[Hodder & Stoughton]] in the 1980s. The first adventure game book of the series, The Wreckers' Tower Game, was published in October 1984.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://enidblytonsociety.co.uk/book-details.php?id=2077&title=The+Wreckers%27+Tower+Game|title=The Wreckers' Tower Game|publisher=The Enid Blyton Society|accessdate=24 April 2014}}</ref>

